cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper discusses the use of deep learning for computer-aided diagnosis of diabetic retinopathy based on retinal fundus images. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of deep learning also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of various image processing techniques, which falls under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
